subfield.desc:
Note
The measured position is :
1. In case of a plot, the measured bias-corrected polar coordinates;
2. In case of a sensor local track, the measured bias-corrected polar co-ordinates of the plot associated to the track;
3. In case of a local track without detection, the extrapolated bias- corrected polar co-ordinates.

Note

     1. XY covariance component = sign {Cov(X,Y)} * sqrt {abs [Cov (X,Y)]}
     2. The maximum value for the (unsigned) XY covariance component is 16.383 km.
